      "para_id": "Q000988.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , whose name was proclaimed by Enlil in Nibru , the steadfast supporter of Enlil's temple , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built ( Enki's ) beloved Abzu for Enki , his beloved master ."
    }
  ],
